&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bioptimus is building the first universal AI foundation model for biology to fuel breakthrough discoveries and accelerate innovation in biomedicine.&amp;nbsp;With more than $75M in funding, Bioptimus is a fast-growing start-up headquartered in Paris, incorporated in October 2023. Backed by leading international venture capitalists, our world-class team of scientists and engineers is redefining the frontiers of AI and life sciences.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clinical Data Manager (Senior)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
