&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Clinical Data Manager, you will operate at the intersection of data engineering, clinical science, and partner collaboration across two strategic domains:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Partner Data Engineering &amp;amp; Collaboration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Partner Interface:&lt;/strong&gt; Participate directly in technical conversations with external partners (hospitals, research institutions, CROs/CMOs). Dive into the details of diverse clinical data structures to understand how data is captured, stored, and extracted.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Order from Uncertainty:&lt;/strong&gt; Translate ambiguous source data into harmonized, AI-ready assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ontology Integration:&lt;/strong&gt; Map and align diverse clinical data to industry-standard biomedical ontologies (e.g., SNOMED, ICD, etc…) with an emphasis on clinical oncology and immunology data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Data Governance, Quality, and Automation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Dictionary Architecture:&lt;/strong&gt; Design

